<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَأَمَّا الأَدِلَّةُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَيُقَدَّمُ الجَلِيُّ مِنْهَا عَلَى الخَفِيِّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَالمُوجِبُ لِلْعِلْمِ عَلَى المُوجِبِ لِلظَّنِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَالنُّطْقُ عَلَى القِيَاسِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَالقِيَاسُ الجَلِيُّ عَلَى القِيَاسِ الخَفِيِّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَإِنْ وُجِدَ فِي النُّطْقِ مَا يُغَيِّرُ الأَصْلَ، وَإِلَّا فَيُسْتَصْحَبُ الحَالُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>